This topic describes how to configure Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) Ops Manager on Azure Government Cloud.

First, complete the steps in [Prepare Azure](./prepare-env-manual.html) and [Deploying BOSH and Ops Manager to Azure Manually](./deploy-manual.html).

Then, follow the procedure for a manual Azure install. In the procedure, select **Azure Government Cloud** in the **Azure Environment** dropdown and set custom VM types.

For the installation procedure, see [Configuring Ops Manager on Azure](config-manual.html).